{"body": "A tax (to be known as land and buildings transaction tax) is to be charged on land transactions.\nThe tax is chargeable\u2014\nwhether or not there is an instrument effecting the transaction,\nif there is such an instrument, whether or not it is executed in Scotland, and\nwhether or not any party to the transaction is present, or resident, in Scotland.\nThe Tax Authority is to be responsible for the collection and management of the tax.", "citation_label": "ASP 2013/11 s. 1", "citation_path": "uk/statute/asp/2013/11/1", "document_class": "statute", "expression_date": "2026-06-07", "heading": "Section 1", "id": "5456fee2-0e18-5393-959e-14f22744a226", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "11", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "1", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "asp", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2013"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "section", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "ASP 2013/11 s. 1", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["S"], "references_to": ["asp/2013/11"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 1, "parent_citation_path": "uk/statute/asp/2013/11", "parent_id": "7e9de6b3-e9cd-51ba-93e4-2b352651e6e1", "source_as_of": "2026-06-07", "source_document_id": "asp/2013/11", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/asp/2013/11/section/1", "source_path": "sources/uk/statute/2026-06-07-uk-lbtt-act-section-1/asp/2013/11/section-1.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/asp/2013/11/section/1", "version": "2026-06-07-uk-lbtt-act-section-1"}
